These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, architect, journalist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, lily, aconite
1. the person who growsdaisy is not to the left of the person who growsaconite##8
2. the journalist is somewhere to the right of the person who growsaconite##5
3. the person who growsaconite is between the architect and the journalist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | architect | analyst   | journalist |
| Flower   | lily | aconite | daisy        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, tea
City: rome, hannover, hamburg
1. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person traveling to rome##7
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
3. the person traveling to hannover is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | tea | cola   | soy-milk   |
| City        | hannover | hamburg | rome |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, trance
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, subway
1. the fan of disco is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
2. the fan of trance is somewhere between the fan of disco and the person driving the bus##7
3. the fan of trance is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
4. the fan of trance is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre        | hip-hop | trance | disco |
| Transport   | bus       | subway     | car         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, architect, bartender
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, amber, purple
1. the bartender is not to the right of the architect##8
2. the bartender is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere between the person who likes amber and the analyst##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | analyst | bartender | architect |
| Color   | purple  | light-blue | amber    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, time-travel
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, punk, indie
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
4. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person watching adventure movies##8
5. the fan of punk is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the fan of indie is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | time-travel | adventure |
| Music-Genre           | punk    | indie      | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, photographer, security-guard
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, classical, dubstep
1. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
2. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
3. the security-guard is not to the right of the fan of pop##8
4. the photographer is on the left of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | photographer | dancer | security-guard |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep        | classical   | pop     |

