.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, sprite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, skiing
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
3. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | sprite |
| Sport        | skiing      | snowboarding    | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-8::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, swimming
1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
2. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##8
3. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
4. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Pet   | rabbit | dog    | lizard |
| Sport         | skiing  | climbing | swimming |

