.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, raspberry, watermelon
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, golf, cricket
1. the person eating pear is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person eating pear##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | pear  | raspberry |
| Sport   | rowing     | golf | cricket   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-10::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, may, june
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, tennis, weightlifting
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
5. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Birthday   | may | june        | september    |
| Sport      | tennis  | weightlifting | biathlon |

