2. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person playing snooker##7
3. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Game   | go     | scrabble | snooker   |
| Hobby      | skydiving | hiking | card-games |

