.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
City: hamburg, san-francisco, prague
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, tennis
1. the person traveling to prague is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
3. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to hamburg##2
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| City   | hamburg       | prague      | san-francisco |
| Sport         | badminton | basketball | tennis     |

