.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, video-games
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
2. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | board-games | magic-tricks | video-games |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | lemonade    | cola    |

 